Affiliation = {Lopes, AV (Corresponding Author), Univ Fed Pernambuco UFPE, Dept Bot, BR-50372970 Recife, PE, Brazil.
   Cruz-Neto, Oswaldo; Tabarelli, Marcelo; Lopes, Ariadna Valentina, Univ Fed Pernambuco UFPE, Dept Bot, BR-50372970 Recife, PE, Brazil.
   Souza e Silva, Jessica Luiza; Woolley, Marcela Masie, Univ Fed Pernambuco UFPE, Programa Posgrad Biol Vegetal, BR-50372970 Recife, PE, Brazil.},
